headline: Avalara Announces $500 Million Investment Led by BlackRock
summary: Avalara, Inc., the agentic tax and compliance leader, today announced it has closed an equity investment from an investor group led by BlackRock's Private Financing Solutions. Vista Equity Partners ("Vista"), which first invested in Avalara in 2022, will remain the company's majority shareholder. All of the proceeds will be used to purchase shares from existing shareholders.

content.title: Avalara Announces $500 Million Investment Led by BlackRock

Vista Equity Partners ("Vista"), which first invested in Avalara in 2022, will remain the company's majority shareholder. All of the proceeds will be used to purchase shares from existing shareholders.

headline: Goldman Says U.S. Stocks Will Continue to Underperform the Rest of the World
summary: Despite a more than 16% rally in the S&P 500 this year, U.S. stocks have been an underperformer on a global scale.  London’s FTSE 100 has returned 21%, while BlackRock’s iShares MSCI Emerging Markets ETF has added over 32%.  Goldman Sachs expects this trend to continue over the next decade.

content.title: Goldman Says U.S. Stocks Will Continue to Underperform the Rest of the World

headline: Dow's new high ahead of House vote, Trump to host Wall Street execs
